<!DOCTYPE html>  
<html lang="en">  
<head>  
    <meta charset="UTF-8">  
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">  
    <title>Welcome to Parking App</title>  
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Link to your CSS file -->  
    <style>  
        body {  
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;  
            margin: 0;  
            padding: 0;  
            background-color: #ffffff;  /* White background */  
            color: #333;  
        }  
        header {  
            background: #ffffff;  /* Green background */  
            color: #302828;  
            padding: 1rem 0;  
            text-align: center;  
            position: relative;  
        }  
        .logo {  
            position: absolute;  
            top: auto;  
            left: 8px;  
            width: 250px;  /* Set the desired width to a larger size */  
            height: auto;  /* Maintain aspect ratio */  
        }  
        .container {  
            width: 80%;  
            margin: auto;  
            overflow: hidden;  
        }  
        .cta {  
            margin: 20px 0;  
            text-align: center;  
        }  
        .cta a {  
            background: #35424a;  
            color: #ffffff;  
            padding: 10px 20px;  
            text-decoration: none;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            transition: background 0.3s;  
        }  
        .cta a:hover {  
            background: #45a049;  
        }  
        .features {  
            display: flex;  
            justify-content: space-around;  
            margin: 20px 0;  
        }  
        .feature {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 20px;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);  
            text-align: center;  
            flex: 1;  
            margin: 10px;  
        }  
    </style>  
</head>  
<body>  
    <header>  
        <img src="../images/parkuy2.png" alt="Parking Logo" class="logo"> <!-- Adjust the path to your logo image -->  
        <h1>Welcome to Parkuy</h1>  
        <h3>Parkir, kuy!</h3>
    </header>  
    <div class="container">  
        <div class="cta">  
            <h2>Your Convenient Parking Solution</h2>  
            <p>Find and book your nearest parking spot quickly and easily.</p>  
            <a href="/register">Get Started</a>  
            <a href="/login" style="margin-left: 10px;">Login</a>  
        </div>  
        <div class="features">  
            <div class="feature">  
                <h3>Easy Registration</h3>  
                <p>Sign up in seconds and start booking parking spots.</p>  
            </div>  
            <div class="feature">  
                <h3>Locate Parking</h3>  
                <p>Use our map feature to find the nearest available parking.</p>  
            </div>  
            <div class="feature">  
                <h3>Secure Payments</h3>  
                <p>Pay securely through our application with ease.</p>  
            </div>  
            <div class="feature">  
                <h3>Your Ticket</h3>  
                <p>Get a digital ticket with a barcode for easy access.</p>  
            </div>  
        </div>  
    </div>  
    <footer>  
        <div style="text-align:center; padding: 20px;">  
            &copy; 2024 Parking Application. All rights reserved.  
        </div>  
    </footer>  
</body>  
</html>